commit.message: ci: add pytestmaster and pytest60 to test matrix
tox: add pytestmaster and pytest60 environments
testing: ignore warning entirely otherwise it interferes with the fnmatching

Also call pytest_runtest_log{start,finish} hooks

Otherwise some reporting is missing.

In particular, pytest 6 moves some output to these hooks.
Use @pytest.hookimpl instead of soft-deprecated @pytest.mark.tryfirst

Change import of getfslineno to be compatible with pytest 6

Really it is private and shouldn't be imported at all, but that's for
another time...

Debugged by Florian Bruhin.
testing: make the atexit monkeypatch more robust, needed for pytest 6
